Ing '''Varosha''' ({{lang-el|Βαρώσια}}; {{lang-tr|Maraş}}) metung yang balayan king e ra kikilalanan a [[w:Northern Cyprus|Republika ning Pangulung Cyprus]] (Republic of Northern Cyprus). Bayu ing [[w:Turkish invasion of Cyprus|pamaniakup da reng Turkes king Cyprus]] aniang 1974, iti ing makabayu nang lugal a pang-turista ning lakanbalen (ciudad) ning [[Famagusta]]. Kareng milabasan a atlung dekada, megi yang [[w:ghost town|balen a melakuan]] (ghost town).

== Pangabanggit king culturang pangmalda (pop culture) ==
Mababanggit ya ing balen king librung ''[[w:The World Without Us|The World Without Us]]'' (St. Martin's Press, 2007) neng Alan Weisman antimong alimbawa ning e tamu apigil a upaya ampong tibe ning kalikasan.

